query.description: (Required) name of the index, you can also provide index date pattern like indexname{2006-01-02}

request.description:
create schema possible values for type[bool|text|date|numeric|geopoint]
golang follows date pattern like indexname{2006-01-02} indexname{2006-01-02} which is equal to {yyyy-MM-dd}
indexname{2006-01-02}-->creates a index every day
indexname{2006-01}-->creates a index every month
indexname{2006}-->creates a index every year

query.description: (Required) name of the index you can also provide pattern like indexName{2006-01-02}-->indexName{yyyy-MM-dd}
index name determind using this date when index name pattern date format must be {yyyy-MM-dd}
